{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"364","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"亞馬遜發現招聘用人工智慧系統歧視女性，決定棄用","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '><img alt='' src='/user_files/news_files/1022.jpg' style='width: 800px; height: 600px;' /></p>\n\n<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>人工智慧系統雖然方便，但運作方式是根據輸入數據來學習，因此一直有研究指出這些系統未必能免除偏見。最近亞馬遜（Amazon）就宣布棄用對女性有歧視問題的招聘用人工智慧系統。</p>\n\n<div class='inside_AD' id='inside_AD' sans='' serif='' style='margin: 40px 0px 0px -15px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; text-align: center; width: 563.266px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>&nbsp;</div>\n\n<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>Amazon 的機器學習團隊自 2014 年以來，就在開發用來審核應徵者履歷表的自動化系統，讓尋找合適人選更簡單。有這樣的系統對已相當自動化的 Amazon 而言並不令人意外。這個系統可為應徵者自動打分數，從一星到五星，就像 Amazon 平台商品，讓人事部快速篩選不合適的人。據消息人士透露，Amazon 原先的目標是要利用人工智慧系統把招聘過程盡量自動化，放入 100 個履歷表後，就自動提供 5 個最合適的人選聘用。</p>\n\n<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>不過這個系統 2015 年被發現分析軟體開發者和其他技術職位的應徵者時，會出現性別偏見。造成這問題的原因，是 Amazon 投入的數據來自 10 年來的聘用紀錄，由於大部分獲聘的都是男性，造成系統直接反映此情況，即履歷表出現「女性」一詞會扣分。雖然 Amazon 嘗試改變系統以減少偏見，但無法確保問題不再出現。</p>\n\n<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>結果去年 Amazon 就棄用這個實驗性系統。Amazon 指，這個系統從來不是決定招聘與否的主要準則。這次事件也證明，要完全去除人工智慧系統對性別和種族的偏見，可能比想像中複雜。</p>\n\n<p sans='' serif='' style='margin: 0px 0px 20px; padding: 0px; font-size: 16.5px; vertical-align: baseline; border: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; clear: both; text-indent: 2em; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微軟正黑體, Arial, STHeiti, '>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p sans='' serif=''>資料來源：https://technews.tw/2018/10/15/amazon-scraps-secret-ai-recruiting-tool-that-showed-bias-against-women/</p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2018-10-22","clk_count":"111"}},"__N_SSG":true}